{"tid":1233682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情緒病婦墮斃 男親友淚別","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T20:23:19.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"304d6066567204712095cef9ccf28ee250e10fd0","tid":1233682,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:23:19.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪婦人墮樓當場身亡，男親友認屍合十淚別！現場順安邨安頌樓，昨清晨六時許，一名女子被發現從上址高處墮樓，直墮大廈對開空地，當場頭部重創昏迷，保安員發現報警求助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190617/photo/0617-00176-058b1.jpg?t=1560716575695\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190617%2Fphoto%2F0617-00176-058b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1560716575695&h=d2c4623a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方及救護員到場，證實女事主已傷重身亡。警方根據死者身上遺物調查，證實事主姓黃（六十歲），隨即聯絡一名卅餘歲男親友到場認屍。據悉，男親友目睹事主遺容時，傷心不已，合十灑淚道別。警方調查事主背景後，獲知有人疑受情緒問題困擾，不排除因此萌生死念。<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190617/00176_058.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190617%2F00176_058.html&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4eSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=7868b792\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190617/00176_058.html</a>"}]}